---
import '../../styles/global.css';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="fr">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <title>Installation | CashierBundle</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>

  <body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="flex">
      <aside class="fixed left-0 top-16 h-[calc(100vh-4rem)] w-64 border-r border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/95 overflow-y-auto p-4">
        <nav class="space-y-1">
          <a href="/docs/installation" class="block rounded-lg bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-2 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-400">Installation</a>
          <a href="/docs/subscriptions" class="block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Abonnements</a>
          <a href="/docs/webhooks" class="block rounded-lg px-3 py-2 text-sm text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Webhooks</a>
        </nav>
      </aside>

      <main class="ml-64 flex-1 p-8 pt-24">
        <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
          <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Installation</h1>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Prérequis</h2>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-slate-400">
              <li>PHP 8.2 ou supérieur</li>
              <li>Symfony 7.0+ ou 8.0+</li>
              <li>Doctrine ORM 3.0+</li>
              <li>Compte Stripe avec clés API</li>
            </ul>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Installation via Composer</h2>
            <pre class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-4 overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-sm">composer require cashier/cashier-bundle</code></pre>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Configuration</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">Ajoutez vos clés Stripe dans le fichier <code>.env</code> :</p>
            <pre class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-4 overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-sm">STRIPE_KEY=pk_test_votre_cle_publique
STRIPE_SECRET=sk_test_votre_cle_secrete
STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_votre_secret_webhook</code></pre>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Configuration du bundle</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">Créez le fichier <code>config/packages/cashier.yaml</code> :</p>
            <pre class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-4 overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-sm">cashier:
    key: '%env(STRIPE_KEY)%'
    secret: '%env(STRIPE_SECRET)%'
    webhook:
        secret: '%env(STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET)%'
        tolerance: 300
    currency: 'usd'
    currency_locale: 'en'
    invoices:
        renderer: 'CashierBundle\Service\InvoiceRenderer\DompdfInvoiceRenderer'</code></pre>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Entité User</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">Faites implémenter <code>BillableEntityInterface</code> à votre entité User.</p>
            <p class="text-slate-400">Utilisez le trait <code>BillableTrait</code> et ajoutez une relation avec <code>StripeCustomer</code>.</p>
          </section>

          <section class="mb-8">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Base de données</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 mb-4">Créez les tables nécessaires :</p>
            <pre class="rounded-lg bg-slate-800 p-4 overflow-x-auto"><code class="text-sm">php bin/console doctrine:migrations:diff
php bin/console doctrine:migrations:migrate</code></pre>
          </section>

          <div class="flex justify-between mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800">
            <a href="/" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">← Accueil</a>
            <a href="/docs/subscriptions" class="text-indigo-400 hover:text-indigo-300">Abonnements →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
